summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Chapter 23.32 of the Seattle Municipal Code at page 118 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone property located at 160 - - 20th Avenue from Lowrise 1 (L1) to Lowrise 3 (L3) (Petition by Mitch Yockey for First Place School, C.F. 310515, DPD Project 3011035).
